<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title>Password Reset</title>
</head>

<body>
	<p>Hi {{firstName}},</p>
	<p>We received a request to reset your password. Use the verification code below to proceed with resetting your
		password:</p>
	<p><strong>{{verificationCode}}</strong></p>
	<p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email or contact support.</p>
	<p>For your security, this code will expire in 15 minutes.</p>
	<p>Thanks,</p>
	<p><strong>Learning Management System Support Team</strong></p>
</body>

</html>